@startuml
title TeacherResource Class Diagram - School Management System

hide circle

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam ClassBorderColor #334155
skinparam ClassBackgroundColor white
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FEF9C3
skinparam NoteBorderColor #A16207

class TeacherResource {
  -id: bigint
  -teacher_id: bigint
  -class_id: bigint
  -category: string
  -name: string
  -description: text
  -original_filename: string
  -file_path: string
  -mime_type: string
  -file_size: bigint
  -download_count: integer

  --
  +allowedCategories(): array
  +teacher(): BelongsTo
  +courseClass(): BelongsTo
}

note right of TeacherResource
TeacherResource represents learning
material uploaded by a teacher for
a specific class group.

The allowedCategories() method defines
the accepted resource categories.
end note

@enduml